ClassDesc: Fields for accessing the Extended Properties. This is a generic set of name/value pairs for use by sync adapters to add extra information to events. There are three writable columns and all three must be present when inserting a new value. They are: @B_android#provider#CalendarContract#ExtendedPropertiesColumns#EVENT_ID_E@ @B_android#provider#CalendarContract#ExtendedPropertiesColumns#NAME_E@ @B_android#provider#CalendarContract#ExtendedPropertiesColumns#VALUE_E@
